data.description: Welcome to this charming one-story in the heart of Killeen. The spacious living room boasts a cozy fireplace and laminate wood flooring. The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself, offering a spacious walk-in closet, private bathroom with extended vanity and dual sinks. The three additional bedrooms provide ample space and comfort. Solar Panels included with home will be paid off by seller at closing.
